# What is it
A game, you need to prevent the ball down to the bottom and break all bricks out.

# build
This project was created on the linux platform and had tested with love2d and tested with WINE.

You can follow steps below on the linux platform to build this project, or just use love2d the run this folder as project.
1. Download love2d
2. Then, you can run it with love2d
3. If you want to build a game for windows platform, you can download "love-11.5-win64.zip" from love2d website, copy the zip file to "./love", and run command `make export_for_win`
